import React from 'react'
import Navbaar from '../Navbaar'
import About from '../About'
import Footer from '../Footer'

function Aboutus() {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbaar/>
      <About/>
      <Footer />
    </>
  )
}
export default Aboutus
